
Beagle is an indexing sub-system and search aggregator built on top of
the Lucene.Net indexer.

For general information on Beagle, visit http://beagle-project.org.

For help on compiling Beagle, visit 
http://www.beagle-project.org/Getting_Started.

If you want to improve or fix Beagle, please read the HACKING file.  

For the latest gossip, visit http://www.beagle-project.org/planet/.

